== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
'''Karigirwa Jeanne d’Arc'''  [yavutse mu mwaka wa 1942]  mu '''[[Rwanda]]''' mu [[Akarere ka Gakenke|aKarere ka Gakenke]] mu [[Intara y’Amajyaruguru y’u Rwanda|intara y'amajyaruguru]]. Akirangiza kwiga [[Amashuri Makuru|amashuri]] [[Amashuli mu Rwanda|abanza]] yahise ajya gukomereza [[Amashuli mu Rwanda|amashuri]] ye yisumbuye i [[Bujumbura]] mu [[Uburundi|Burundi]].Mu 1966 yaje kugaruka mu [[Rwanda]] kubera ko ariho hari ababyeyi be. Bitewe n’[[ubuzima]] bari babayeho bwo gutotezwa, '''Kaligirwa''' yaje gufata umwanzuro wo guhungira mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]] mu 1972. Nyuma y’[[umwaka]] [[Rimwe|umwe]] gusa, mu 1973 yakoresheje uburyo bwose bushoboka akura [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|umuryango]] we mu [[Rwanda]] umusanga mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]].<ref>https://umuseke.rw/2021/07/kaligirwa-wanditse-turaje-indege-irahinda-na-girubuntu-zaririmbwe-nitorero-isamaza-ni-muntu-ki/amp/</ref><ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/umuhanzi-nyiranyamibwa-yaje-gutura-i-kigali-nyuma-y-imyaka-40-aba-mu-mahanga?fbclid=IwAR2f-KVFgmLRJZ3oshzGkpQXaW6OJyarqUbLfGC7HqOOOvvH4Da-lO8dd4M</ref>

== MURI MUZIKA ==


'''Karigirwa Jeanne d'Arc'''  wari ufite impano yo kwandika [[Indirimbo y’igihugu|indirimbo]] no kuririmba yafashe ikaramu ye maze yandika [[Indirimbo y’igihugu|indirimbo]] ayita “[[Rwanda|Rw'''anda''']] '''turanze twanze guhera ishyanga'''” mu mwaka wa 1989. Icyo gihe nibwo yatangiye guhuza abiganjemo [[Umugore|abagore]] n’[[Umugore|inkumi]] muri abo abamenyekanye cyane ni [[Nyiranyamibwa Suzana|Nyiranyamibwa Suzanne]], '''Anonciata Gatera''', umuvandimwe we '''Françoise Ruboneka''', '''Anonciata Kayisire''' n’abandi batandukanye maze bashinga [[Umuziki gakondo w'u Rwanda|itorero Isamaza]]. Iyo iba imvo n’imvano y’ishingwa ry[[Umuziki gakondo w'u Rwanda|’itorero Isamaza]]’ ryari rigamije gutiza umurindi [https://www.mod.gov.rw/ ingabo] z’Inkotanyi<ref>https://www.mod.gov.rw/</ref> no kuzishakira ubufasha bwo kuzishyigikira mu rugamba rwo kubohora [[igihugu]].<ref>https://umuseke.rw/2021/07/kaligirwa-wanditse-turaje-indege-irahinda-na-girubuntu-zaririmbwe-nitorero-isamaza-ni-muntu-ki/amp/</ref><ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/umuhanzi-nyiranyamibwa-yaje-gutura-i-kigali-nyuma-y-imyaka-40-aba-mu-mahanga?fbclid=IwAR2f-KVFgmLRJZ3oshzGkpQXaW6OJyarqUbLfGC7HqOOOvvH4Da-lO8dd4M</ref>

